@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_uppnph(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.cos(v0)
    v0 = (((v2 + 0.48 / v1 + 0.97) - (v0 + 0.27 - v1 + 0.15)) / wp.exp(0.93))
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v2 + 0.64)) - (wp.cos(tmp + 0.21) - (v2 + 0.70 * v2 + 0.28)))
    v0 = 0.15
    v2 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
